original_name: Jamie Foxx Presents - America's Funniest Comics Volume 1
name: Jamie Foxx Presents - America's Funniest Comics Volume 1
overview: Foxx returns to his comedy roots. Filmed before a live audience at Atlanta's hottest urban comedy and arts festival, Foxx hand picks the best up and comers with the freshest material and and the most unbelievable jokes ever heard. Cedric the Entertainer hosts.
